Elles disent : le
                       Louvre, la place Royale, mais elles usent de tours et de phrases plutôt
                    que de prononcer de certains noms ;

or if by chance they
                       let such a word slip, they will excuse it  as if it
                       were criminal;

goes every day to  Morning and Evening Prayer;
                     "Feuillants" and 'Minimes" refer to the congregations
                       celebrating the mass, not the time of the day when it takes place.
